</groundspeak:long_description><groundspeak:encoded_hints>No need to go into the woods.</groundspeak:encoded_hints><groundspeak:logs><groundspeak:log id="1364248315"><groundspeak:date>2026-05-29T17:17:12</groundspeak:date><groundspeak:type>Found it</groundspeak:type><groundspeak:finder id="44063352">Babyseals63</groundspeak:finder><groundspeak:text encoded="false">Thanks for the find! With CMA8 crew!</groundspeak:text></groundspeak:log><groundspeak:log id="1364254035"><groundspeak:date>2026-05-29T12:00:00</groundspeak:date><groundspeak:type>Found it</groundspeak:type><groundspeak:finder id="79259">BlackstoneVal</groundspeak:finder><groundspeak:text encoded="false">NY Cache Odyssey visited while on our way back home from GeoWoodstock.  Swapped trackables placing Route 66 which would like to go back west bound.
Val and Mar from New England with CMA8</groundspeak:text></groundspeak:log><groundspeak:log id="1364251397"><groundspeak:date>2026-05-29T12:00:00</groundspeak:date><groundspeak:type>Write note</groundspeak:type><groundspeak:finder id="135681">Scout338</groundspeak:finder><groundspeak:text encoded="false">From Central MA.  Working our way back home from GeoWoodstock.  We got this Odyssey last year on our way home from GeoWoodstock in West Virginia with RandN916.  This year we have our other friends and family here to get it. It was fun to see them wander around to find it. Thanks for the fun. Scout338😁</groundspeak:text></groundspeak:log><groundspeak:log id="1364249059"><groundspeak:date>2026-05-29T12:00:00</groundspeak:date><groundspeak:type>Found it</groundspeak:type><groundspeak:finder id="553797">~Marvalus</groundspeak:finder><groundspeak:text encoded="false">Part of the CMA8 Crew had found this previously, but since we were meandering our way home after geowoodstock, we wanted to grab it for the rest of us! TFTC</groundspeak:text></groundspeak:log><groundspeak:log id="1364248695"><groundspeak:date>2026-05-29T12:00:00</groundspeak:date><groundspeak:type>Found it</groundspeak:type><groundspeak:finder id="855331">RustyRose</groundspeak:finder><groundspeak:text encoded="false">We are traveling in a group of 8 from Massachusetts!!! Signed our logs CMA8!!! We are on our last leg heading home working on states!!! We are coming back from Kansas Geo Woodstock!! Thanks!!!🙂</groundspeak:text></groundspeak:log></groundspeak:logs></groundspeak:cache></wpt><wpt lat="39.4112" lon="-77.406617"><time>2024-10-17T00:00:00</time><name>GCAZACH</name><desc>Cache Odyssey - Maryland by Always Lost 00</desc><url>https://www.geocaching.com/geocache/GCAZACH</url><urlname>Cache Odyssey - Maryland</urlname><sym>Geocache</sym><type>Geocache|Letterbox Hybrid</type><groundspeak:cache id="9727819" available="true" archived="false"><groundspeak:name>Cache Odyssey - Maryland</groundspeak:name><groundspeak:placed_by>Always Lost 00</groundspeak:placed_by><groundspeak:owner id="566911">Always Lost 00</groundspeak:owner><groundspeak:type>Letterbox Hybrid</groundspeak:type><groundspeak:container>Large</groundspeak:container><groundspeak:attributes><groundspeak:attribute id="24" inc="1">Wheelchair accessible</groundspeak:attribute><groundspeak:attribute id="6" inc="1">Recommended for kids</groundspeak:attribute><groundspeak:attribute id="41" inc="1">Stroller accessible</groundspeak:attribute><groundspeak:attribute id="67" inc="1">GeoTour</groundspeak:attribute><groundspeak:attribute id="13" inc="0">Available 24/7</groundspeak:attribute><groundspeak:attribute id="7" inc="1">Takes less than one hour</groundspeak:attribute><groundspeak:attribute id="25" inc="1">Parking nearby</groundspeak:attribute><groundspeak:attribute id="47" inc="1">Field puzzle</groundspeak:attribute><groundspeak:attribute id="63" inc="1">Recommended for tourists</groundspeak:attribute><groundspeak:attribute id="28" inc="1">Public restrooms nearby</groundspeak:attribute></groundspeak:attributes><groundspeak:difficulty>1.5</groundspeak:difficulty><groundspeak:terrain>1</groundspeak:terrain><groundspeak:country>United States</groundspeak:country><groundspeak:state>Maryland</groundspeak:state><groundspeak:short_description /><groundspeak:long_description>&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://img.geocaching.com:443/085ef39f-7673-44fc-945f-3579422587dc.png" width="100%" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

